        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Saving to the database alone is insufficient if the Claude API gate caches preferences in memory. A change propagation mechanism ensures that a user disabling a feature in the UI causes that feature to stop being called within seconds, not at the next cache TTL expiry."
          }
