            "type": "text",
            "text": "A preference center for Claude settings requires a versioned flat preference schema, a merge-friendly PATCH API, a typed storage layer with UPSERT semantics, and a consumption layer that applies toggles and style preferences at the API gate. Audit logging records the full history of preference changes, and a pub-sub propagation mechanism ensures that changes reach all consumers within seconds. Together these components give users genuine control over their AI experience while giving the enterprise the audit trail needed to demonstrate that control was real and respected."
